<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/849714-this-is-being-touted-as-book-to-explain">This is being touted as book to explain the rise of Trump in this country.

Does it explain it? 

Trump has never said exactly how he will deliver on his promise to make America great again. Why do Appalachians believe empty promises, especially from wealthy (well, if he would release his taxes we&#39;d know for sure) businessmen? Is it wishful thinking?</a>
</div>
