<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/819444-this-is-a-hard-read-i-am-53-years-old">This is a hard read. I am 53 years old and just finished this book yesterday. I have cried all day yesterday, all night woke with nightmares and am crying now. I know this is for questions. The only question I have is... does it ever get ok?</a>
</div>
