    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1879047010" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1879047010" />
    <a title="Jessaka" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4659464-jessaka"><img alt="Jessaka" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1485709659p2/4659464.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1879047010?book_show_action=true">Jan 14, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jessaka" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jessaka" href="/user/show/4659464-jessaka">Jessaka</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4659464-jessaka?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4659464-jessaka?shelf=politics">politics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1879047010" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3346929043121964545">HILLBILLY ELEGIST: YOUR BOOK SMELLS BAD ENOUGH TO KNOCKA BUZZARD OFF A SHIT WAGON<br/><br/>Ma lives in the holler<br/>way back yander thar.<br/>she plays the fiddle and sings<br/>just like Emmy Lou.<br/><br/>Mamaw chews tobacco<br/>and spits the wad right <br/>in her old Styrofoam cup.<br/>even in front of company.<br/><br/>my pa was a coal miner<br/>and beats us younguns <br/>cus he meaner than a polecat<br/>and a little touched<br/>when he is drunker <br/>than Cootey Brown.<br/><br/>We refused welfare <br/>don&apos;t believe in eating<br/>high on the hog,<br/>so I picked my poor self up<br/>and so can y&apos;all. <br/>ju</span>
  <span id="freeText3346929043121964545" style="display:none">HILLBILLY ELEGIST: YOUR BOOK SMELLS BAD ENOUGH TO KNOCKA BUZZARD OFF A SHIT WAGON<br /><br />Ma lives in the holler<br />way back yander thar.<br />she plays the fiddle and sings<br />just like Emmy Lou.<br /><br />Mamaw chews tobacco<br />and spits the wad right <br />in her old Styrofoam cup.<br />even in front of company.<br /><br />my pa was a coal miner<br />and beats us younguns <br />cus he meaner than a polecat<br />and a little touched<br />when he is drunker <br />than Cootey Brown.<br /><br />We refused welfare <br />don't believe in eating<br />high on the hog,<br />so I picked my poor self up<br />and so can y'all. <br />just go out and git a job <br />cus it is y'alls falt <br />if y'all ain't a workin'<br /><br />And if you read this far<br />I got your attention<br />so I want to say that <br />this here writer feller <br />plumb needs some more book larnin,<br />and a whole lotta more empathy.<br /><br />He makes me fit to be tied;<br />I am madder than a wet hornet.<br />cus getting anywhere in life<br />takes luck and opportunity.<br />and that means it has to<br />come up and bite you <br />in the butt. <br /><br />it isn't always their fault<br />if they are down and out,<br />but now you have written<br />a book for republicans<br />to use against your kinfolk.<br /><br />written by Jessica Slade, 2017</span>
